## 🟢 New Features to Build

### 11. Password Reset Flow
You already have OTP + email + Redis. Add:
- `POST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password` → send OTP to email
- `POST /api/v1/auth/reset-password` → verify OTP + set new password

### 12. Profile Update Endpoint
- `PUT /api/v1/users/profile` → update name, image
- `PUT /api/v1/users/change-password` → change password (requires old password)

### 13. Product System
- Product model (name, description, price, category, images, stock)
- `GET /api/v1/products` — list/search/filter products
- `GET /api/v1/products/:id` — product detail

### 14. Cart System
- Cart model (user, items, quantities)
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/cart` — CRUD operations

### 15. Wishlist
- `GET/POST/DELETE /api/v1/wishlist`

### 16. Order Management
- Order model (user, items, total, status, address)
- `POST /api/v1/orders` — place order
- `GET /api/v1/orders` — order history
- `GET /api/v1/orders/:id` — order detail

### 17. Address Management
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/users/addresses`

