1. Fix Bearer token parsing          ← 2 minutes, breaks all standard clients
2. Fix User.insertOne → User.create  ← 1 minute, may crash at runtime
3. Fix inconsistent response key     ← 1 minute
4. Add input validation              ← 30 minutes, prevents bad data
5. Add Helmet + Morgan               ← 5 minutes, security + debugging
6. Centralized error handler         ← 20 minutes, cleaner code
7. Password reset flow               ← 1 hour, you have the building blocks
8. Profile update endpoints          ← 30 minutes
